Day 27: Encourage Cross-Functionality!
🔧 "A cross-functional team is an unstoppable team!"  
👉 Tip: Promote cross-functional skills within your team. The more skills the team shares, the more flexible and adaptable they become.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
